    <stitle>TSI 97-12-20R - Glow Plug Relay Service Package</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi971220R" tsitype="engine">
        <tsinumber>97-12-20R</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>January, 1999</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>ENGINE</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Glow Plug Relay Service Package</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <engfamgroup/>

                <engfam>T 444E</engfam>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>A new glow plug relay designed for extended service part life is released for the T 444E engine.
                    The new glow plug relay Part No.
                    <emph type="bold">1831646C1</emph>
                    replaces the current relays, Part Nos.
                    <emph type="bold">1825908C2</emph>,
                    <emph type="bold">1807230C2</emph>
                    and
                    <emph type="bold">1825931C2</emph>. Also available is a field service conversion package Part No.
                    <emph type="bold">1826634C94</emph>. An adapter wire (furnished in the package with a drawing) is
                    required to connect the new relay to the engine electrical harness.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <important>
                        <para>Be sure to follow the instructions furnished with the package.</para>
                    </important>
                </specpara>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
